{
  "id": "adv_card_mna_53_03",
  "title": "長瀬麻奈",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "ネックレスが元通りになっているってことは\nビーズが全部見つかったのね。良かったわ～",
      "startTime": 4.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "いえ。そこからまた一時間以上探したんですけど\n結局、あの一粒しか見つからなかったんです",
      "startTime": 13.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "でも……次の日、朝起きると\n机の上にお姉ちゃんにあげたのと\nそっくりなビーズのネックレスが二本置かれてて……",
      "startTime": 23.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5566.666666699998,
          "startTime": 29.1666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.55
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.55
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-01.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁ～、おはよう、琴乃～！　早起きだね～",
      "startTime": 30.4333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_enter-01.m4a",
      "text": "せっかく旅館に泊まってるし朝風呂行かない？",
      "startTime": 34.9999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.4666662852
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "お、お姉ちゃん！　なんでネックレスが……！？\nビーズは見つからなかったのに……",
      "startTime": 42.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.4999996185
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_emb-03.m4a",
      "text": "私にくれたネックレス、とっても長かったでしょ？",
      "startTime": 45.4999996185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-04.m4a",
      "text": "解いたら二本になるかな～って思って！　はい、どうぞ",
      "startTime": 49.3197838227,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3080.2161772999953,
          "startTime": 52.4
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4880.2161773,
          "startTime": 54.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.3197838227
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.8666678111
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう、あれ？\nこのネックレス、星型のペンダントも付いてる……！",
      "startTime": 60.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.1000008901
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-10.m4a",
      "text": "そう。お土産物屋さんで琴乃が見ていた星のペンダント",
      "startTime": 64.1000008901,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-07.m4a",
      "text": "私も素敵だな～って思ったから付けてみたんだ！",
      "startTime": 68.3402793776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.6999988556
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sorry-01.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと短くなっちゃったし、元通りではないけど",
      "startTime": 72.6999988556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-04.m4a",
      "text": "形は変わっても琴乃とお揃いなことは変わらないでしょ",
      "startTime": 76.7531204621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.5333418528
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん……！\n私このネックレス、一生大事にする！　宝物にするよ！",
      "startTime": 84.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_evening",
      "startTime": 90.8166777293
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ！　思い出した！　そのネックレス麻奈ちゃんが\n雑誌の誕生日インタビューで紹介してたものだわ！",
      "startTime": 96.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "その雑誌、私も読んでみたかったです。お姉ちゃん\nこのネックレスのことなんて言ってたんだろう……",
      "startTime": 105.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "もしかしたら私の部屋にあるかも……\nちょっと待ってて、探してくるわ！",
      "startTime": 113.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3599.9874114999957,
          "startTime": 113.0666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4166.666666599994,
          "startTime": 117.2333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8833.333333300005,
          "startTime": 121.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "お待たせ、見つけたわよ～！　確か私も小さくスナップ\nを載せてもらってたのよ。懐かしいわね～",
      "startTime": 123.9868470495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "『誕生日特別企画、長瀬麻奈に聞きたい十八の質問』\n雑誌の表紙から見開きまで、全部お姉ちゃんだ……凄い",
      "startTime": 135.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "予約だけで完売しちゃって、発売前に異例の増刷が\n決まったり、発売後も手に入れるのが一苦労だったのよ",
      "startTime": 146.0333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5366.666666700013,
          "startTime": 151.4
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10333.33333340002,
          "startTime": 156.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……麻奈ちゃんがそのネックレスについて\n話していたインタビュー記事は……あった。ここだわ！",
      "startTime": 155.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8300.000000000011,
          "startTime": 163.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
