    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "「四つ目の質問です。麻奈さんが今までで一番\n嬉しかった誕生日プレゼントはなんですか？」",
      "startTime": 170.900008138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "「私を想って選んでくれた物はなんでも嬉しいので\n決められません。でも一番印象的だったのは――」",
      "startTime": 178.6333414714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 184.566692988
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "「大好きな妹がくれた手作りのビーズのネックレスです\n私のことを想って作ってくれたのがすっごく嬉しくて」",
      "startTime": 190.700008138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 195.866692988
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "「お母さんから聞いたんですけど、色んなお店を回って\n私の好きそうなビーズを集めてくれたらしいんですよ」",
      "startTime": 200.800008138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 205.2666970569
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_03-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "「一粒一粒に妹から私への愛が伝わってきて……\nすみません、えへへ、涙が……」",
      "startTime": 211.9666748047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
